summary: An Ordinance providing for the improvement of East Jefferson Street, in the City of Seattle, from Twentieth Avenue to a point one hundred six (106) feet east of Twenty-third Avenue, by constructing concrete sidewalks, in accordance with Resolution No. 1533 of the City Council of the City of Seattle, and providing for the payment therefor by the mode of "Payment by Bonds," as provided by the laws of the State of Washington and the Charter and Ordinances of the City of Seattle
